# GymBuddy AI – no API keys or secrets are required for the current build.
# All data is stored in the browser (localStorage). If you add server-side
# features (e.g. auth, DB, external APIs), put secrets in .env.local and
# never commit them. Add variable names here without values, e.g.:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_OPTIONAL_FEATURE=
# SECRET_API_KEY=
